creator: Armstrong Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Only available in Jordan.

Tanda is a fully digital, mobile, financial solutions provider, which aims to promote financial inclusion in the MENA region through the facilitation of different solutions through its platform.

Our flagship solution is a digital ROSCA whereby users can organise and join informal saving clubs and manage their finances.

Sign up in just a few minutes

You can create an account in just a few clicks to set up your saving club and invite your family and friends.

Easy and safe transactions

You can now receive and send your ROSCA payments directly through your secure Dinarak© mobile wallet.

Track your payments and payouts

Through a simple interface Tanda takes on the hassle of organizing your payments and payouts through an embedded reminder and tracking system.

Join our growing community and enjoy our service offerings

Tanda will not stop here, our team is dedicated to roll-out products and features that will change the way you save, spend, and manage your finances.

We hear you! So please share with us your feedback, wish list, comments, and suggestions
descriptionShort: This release brings to life Tanda's flagship product, a digital ROSCA.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Add new features.
- Security enhancement : sign-out after idle period.
- General bug fixing.
